text: Gert Voss (10 October 1941 - 13 July 2014) was a German actor. He was known for his roles in Der Kopf des Mohren (1995), Doktor Knock (1996) and Ritter, Dene, Voss (1987). He was born in Shanghai, China. Voss died in Vienna, Austria from leukemia, aged 72. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1941 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Deaths from leukemia Category:Cancer deaths in Austria Category:German movie actors Category:German television actors Category:Actors from Shanghai
